name: Completion Date
title: CD
definition: Identifies the date on which the ASR (PON) was completed by the provider, service was activated and billing may commence.

validEntry.description: Two Digit Month (01-12) Two Digit Century (00-99)
Two Digit Day (01-31) Two Digit Year (00-99)
Two Digit Century (00-99) Two Digit Month (01-12)
Two Digit Year (00-99) Two Digit Day (01-31)

validEntryNotes: Metric date format may be used based on customer/provider negotiations.
usageNotes: Required when the CNT field is “A”, otherwise prohibited.
